Airbnb launches free currency trading
text:
I made €86.4 trading currencies on Airbnb:

Made a booking priced in $ at $740 in November 2021. I am based in Europe, my bank account is in €. I was charged €648.5

I canceled the booking in July 2022. They refunded me the $740. It converted to €734.9

Made €86 :))
